Name: Axis_Values
Description: The Axis_Values class describes the values which are associated with the elements along an axis of a observation data array.

Name: axis_number
Description: The index of the axis. The first axis is numbered as 1.

Name: Face_Values
Description: The Face_Values class describes the values which are associated with the elements on the face of a observation data array.

Name: Face_Plane
Description: The Face_Plane class describes a plane which is defined by two axes.

Name: face_axis
Description: The axis number that defines one axis of a face plane.

Name: Local_Internal_Reference
Description: The Local_Internal_Reference class is used to cross-reference other classes or objects within the product.

Name: local_identifier_reference
Description: The local_identifier_reference attribute provides the value of the local_identifier of the entity described by the referencing class. Note that a local_identifier attribute, with the same value as this local_identifier_reference, must be present within the label.

Name: local_reference_type
Description: The local_reference_type attribute provides the name of an association between an entity identified by a local_identifier_reference and another corresponding entity identified by a local_identifier

Name: wave_observation_to_observation_values
Description: A reference to the array containing the primary observation data.

Name: wave_observation_to_axis_values
Description: A reference to the array containing the data values for an axis of primary observation data.

Name: wave_observation_to_face_values
Description: A reference to the array containing the data values for a face of primary observation data.

Name: comment
Description: The comment attribute is a character string expressing one or more remarks or thoughts relevant to the object.

Name: Wave_Observation
Description: The Wave_Observation describes the data of a observation and the values which are associated with the elements along an axis or on the face of a observation data array.

Name: name
Description: The name attribute provides a word or combination of words by which the object is known.

Name: local_identifier
Description: The local_identifier attribute provides a character string which uniquely identifies the containing object within the label.

Name: description
Description: The description attribute provides a statement, picture in words, or account that describes or is otherwise relevant to the object.

Name: Primary_Values
Description: The Primary_Values class describes the values which are the primary observation data array.
